Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time, a very wise fisherman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,picked up a small pot at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When the fisherman opened the lid,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a very big devil came out of that small pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A hungry devil tried to eat fisherman right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fisherman who was taken aback said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Did you really come out of that pot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil showed his power to that fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Smaller!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The fisherman was planning to put the devil back into the pot if he had gotten smaller again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the devil noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Surely you can't drink all that ocean water up even if you were capable of everything, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil who got angry by the fisherman's words started drinking ocean water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey! More! Drink some more!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fisherman got rid of the bad devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous person's wisdom can outdo any kind of violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Devil Garon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An object that fell on the northern Alps at about 11:20 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,caused a forest fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fire department is putting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The fallen object seems to be a massive meteor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and Doctor Ochanomizu's team is heading to the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, investigate whether there is any radioactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is faint radioactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not high enough to affect human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite heavy. It dug a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The depth is about 120 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All trees have fallen in a radial shape due to the falling shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, go down and dig the meteor out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, would it be all right for a mere robot to dig it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call Atom a "mere robot," Dr.Amanogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Don't break or destroy the meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's buried really deep. It must be down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still got some heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been heated up since it passed through the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This isn't a meteor? Someone built this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wh, what is that, Atom? -I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, this isn't an earthly matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. This is really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope something weird doesn't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It opens here. It comes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's even more confusing after disassembling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a jigsaw puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, this and this go together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And this and this. Huh? Dr.Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, could you assemble this with your computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it, Dr.Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all done, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even use screws and they fit well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems like a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Robot? -Robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? An assembly robot fell from space?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in which planet sent this to earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not interesting to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This part doesn't fit anywhere in that space robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't fit anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be... some kind of recording tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, could you translate it with your computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Promised Garon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-Garon? -So that one's name is Garon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We will send it to Megaropa for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This can kill plusters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and renovate all matters in your planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From the king of Yura to the minister of Megaropa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill plusters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like it can kill some kind of creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon must have fallen to the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,due to some kind of error that happened while it was being transported.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've picked up a ridiculous thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'd like to test it to see how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Garon must be disassembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need a robot that kills or renovates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,something on the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Disassemble it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no sense to destroy such precious science data.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't know what kind of harm it would cause to humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can always disassemble it when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't follow our commands, we can disassemble it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for you to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, keep Garon accompanied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Amanogawwa! What do you think you are saying to Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to disassemble Garon no matter what. We don't need Garon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots like Atom are necessary for this Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are a robot just like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, it seems like we have completely different opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to know a scientist like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get Garon no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ministry of Science won't allow you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like there's going to be a storm. Come inside the tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a fight with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as stubborn as a mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, please disassemble Garon later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon isn't a robot we need for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, are you okay with thunders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. What about you? Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I don't mind such thun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate thunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Dr.Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, did you see that? -Garon moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon! You came to Earth by a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So please go back to your original form quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else people on Earth will get in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying, Garon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You are so violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Garon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a power to change an entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I cannot fight against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Put Garon in this hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned surrounding rocks into magma
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with the heat wave it emitted itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Amanogawa, a disparate matter reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was caught in the radar 200 meters up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon's been buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to knock Ochanomizu down for sure with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to disassemble it and transport it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Be careful! -Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even magma has cooled down around the area where Garon fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Garon cannot be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have gotten deeper underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue to be on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world has Garon gone to? It's been 20 weeks already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon! Look at this island carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is deserted. There are only palm trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and renovate this place as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it look like the planet you used to live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. Go ahead and film this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Record it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is beyond expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see how a far-end planet looks like on this Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc...Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the rock Garon has renovated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. This is platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon, you really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has turned this deserted island into a platinum island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With this much platinum in my hand, I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, something's wrong with the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Analyze the atmosphere. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 70% of nitrogen and 20% of ammonia included in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? What about oxygen? -Only 0.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops... It has renovated even the atmosphere like that of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon, where are you? It's a command. Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, no more! Let's go back to the plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was foolish. Even though it was trained,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a monster is a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost every living thing was wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The suffocating gas that occurred at the southern ocean is spreading fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Three islands have already been affected and there are numerous victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Passenger liner Gloria which was sailing nearby also has lost its contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that it has also gotten affected by that gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, this is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This gas will affect the entire Earth very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find out the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As a robot, you are fit for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-You understand, right? -Of course, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu! Seagulls carcass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison gas seems to be near. It's getting thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I see the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a strange island. It doesn't look like Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a collapsed one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr.Amanogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Dr.Amanogawa? Why would he be in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Garon's deed for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a trace that Garon has melted with a high heat wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Garon nearby? Be careful, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon! I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon, so it's you who are emitting this poisonous gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No! You can't do such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the world peace. I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A hydrogen bomb? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Garon would be finished if we use hydrogen bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the radiation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The army has decided already. They probably started the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what would happen to Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Atom, hurry and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A hydrogen bomb missile is flying there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I hear the missile sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! The missile has turned into gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My gosh. There's nothing that can defeat that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our best air force is charging in right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's no use to fight against Garon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please stop the attack! -But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something wise in mind, Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, in one of fairy tales, there is a story in which
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a fisherman who was about to be eaten
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by the devil defeats the powerful devil with his wisdom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to test that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Atom, try then. I wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon! Listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were probably planning to renovate even the atmosphere of this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is one important thing remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to tell you what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gravity! The Earth's gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to create a planet like the one you used to live in, change the gravity as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Change the gravity for even one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really going to do it. Can he really change gravity as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Garon can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Only for a minute! Change the gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, Garon's focusing on changing the gravity right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ask him to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If the planet's gravity is smaller than the Earth's, then the gravity there will decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atom, what happened? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr.Ochanomizu, can you hear me? It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The part of the island with decreased gravity was cut out; I can't even find a trace of Garon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If the gravity decreases only on that island,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the air gets lighter there and goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the surrounding air is driven toward there like a typhoon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and whatever that is on that island goes up in sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like launching a rocket; it goes right up to the stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With that force, it gets out of the Earth's gravity zone and directly flies into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't the atmosphere of that place continue to fly away to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I told him to change it only for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Garon decreased gravity only for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom's wisdom won against force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If Garon were delivered to the right place, he would have used his power rightfully, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know how fearful it is to use your power incorrectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire fighter robot Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The nurse robot Lilli.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The welder robot Pitato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all abandoned by human and were sent to junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They can still work though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And a big fire breaks out in the space factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up! Now is the time to show your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Hurry, You Three Second-Rate Knights"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
